    "text": "Awesome series by @warmanwardhani (via our friends from @discoverearth) \u2014 If you\u2019re looking for alternative things to do around Yogyakarta then Kedung Kayang Waterfall should be on your list of things to do. Let me tell you a bit about this natural attraction that\u2019s just a few hours from Yogyakarta. It makes for a nice alternative day trip from Yogyakarta. Looks like a place worth visiting. \u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800\u2800 Tag #AllAboutAdventures for a chance to be featured!",
